{"tid":653407,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"6成警察屬「假貨」　非法分子冒警混入墨西哥一城市警察總部","createTime":"2018-05-04T16:35:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-06T09:01:50.000Z","uid":53379,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"eb67718e4996853820a192510e384f973e2ad42d","tid":653407,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T16:35:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">6成警察屬「假貨」　非法分子冒警混入墨西哥一城市警察總部</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180504/s00005/a980dee308b0225960fa23f54070af97.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180504%2Fs00005%2Fa980dee308b0225960fa23f54070af97.jpg&h=e335d7cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n墨西哥中部城市警察總部185名警察中，有113人都是「冒牌警察」！墨西哥檢察官日前搜查普埃布拉州（Puebla）中部城市聖馬丁特斯梅盧坎（San Martin Texmelucan）的警察總部，發現當中的185名警察，有113人屬冒充，震驚當地。<br />\n<br />\n警察總部中，有數名真正的警察收受155至260元美金（約港幣1,216至2,040元），讓那些想逃避背景審查及避免遭逮捕的人可冒充警察。<br />\n<br />\n普埃布拉州公共安全部指，113名「冒牌警察」將被控冒充警察等罪名，州政府亦會接管聖馬丁特斯梅盧坎的警務。<br />\n<br />\n普埃布拉州有大量由犯罪集團鑽探的非法油管，以竊取政府擁有的柴油或汽油。另外，墨西哥已有幾個州份的警察隊伍，由於被發現貪污腐敗，已遭解散。<br />\n<br />\n(自由時報/The Province)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180504/s00005/1525427659501\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180504%2Fs00005%2F1525427659501&d=LiGpq4PHcy29c2DU02GkF0zHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=8d89e44a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180504%2Fs00005%2F1525427659501&h=1cd33580\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180504/s00005/1525427659501</a>"},{"pid":"c1a52539ca9f9817058b4846e82f4622025a36c1","tid":653407,"uid":65603,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T16:39:52.000Z","msg":"Cls警隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a3ba8e6bfff5c840ee7